Provenance: these cohorts are derived from U.S. CDC BRFSS public-use files
(LLCP2021.XPT, LLCP2015.XPT), which are in the U.S. federal public domain. The
derivation steps are documented in data/PROVENANCE.md. Attribution to CDC is
retained as the authoritative upstream source.
